{"tid":1878373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★46 48 49 52 53個案於北角明星海鮮酒家一同聚餐。","createTime":"2020-02-13T14:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T15:14:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3e9833b2cc6480bdeaacc0cb9f90a54d3e7cfd43","tid":1878373,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:28:37.000Z","msg":"衞生署衞生防護中心公布，再多兩宗確診，連同早前屯門醫院個案紫田村患者，累計53宗。<br />\n<br />\n兩宗個案涉及一對母子，分別為67歲女子（為第52宗個案）及37歲男子（為第53宗個案）。兩人於1月26日（年初二）晚上與早前確診的三名病人（第46、48及49宗個案，即長青邨康美樓母子及新抱）於北角明星海鮮酒家一同出席聚餐。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/433921/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%94%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%B0%8F%E5%A7%A8%E5%A4%96%E7%94%A5%E9%A3%AF%E8%81%9A%E5%9D%87%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F433921%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E7%2594%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%2582%25A3%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25A7%25A8%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%2594%25A5%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E8%2581%259A%25E5%259D%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%258B%259B&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=8e049b31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/433921/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E5%86%8D%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%A9%E5%AE%97%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%94%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%B0%8F%E5%A7%A8%E5%A4%96%E7%94%A5%E9%A3%AF%E8%81%9A%E5%9D%87%E4%B8%AD%E6%8B%9B</a>"},{"pid":"e30ce284a0fab4673af2039200dded9ef64b626f","tid":1878373,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocki